    <FlavorTextDef>
        <InternalName>LuxarDominion_Warning_CosmicContaminant</InternalName>
        <FlavorTextOption>
            <Requirements>
                <ListenerHasUniversalTranslator>false</ListenerHasUniversalTranslator>
                <PlayerMustKnowSpeaker>false</PlayerMustKnowSpeaker>
                <PlayerMustKnowListener>true</PlayerMustKnowListener>
            </Requirements>
            <Text>卢克萨统治领继续向银河系社群发出警告，关于一个被他们称为“宇宙污染体”的团体。统治领描述了一个由敌对且迅速变异的生物组成的有组织集团，这些生物在辐射中茁壮成长。</Text>
        </FlavorTextOption>
    </FlavorTextDef>

    <FlavorTextDef>
        <InternalName>Korath_Declaration_TrueInheritors</InternalName>
        <FlavorTextOption>
            <Requirements>
                <ListenerHasUniversalTranslator>false</ListenerHasUniversalTranslator>
                <PlayerMustKnowSpeaker>false</PlayerMustKnowSpeaker>
                <PlayerMustKnowListener>true</PlayerMustKnowListener>
            </Requirements>
            <Text>科拉思氏族宣称自己是德伦金帝国真正的继承者。作为德伦金帝国的冲锋兵，科拉思以残忍无情的行为而闻名。他们公开誓言要消灭所有生命。</Text>
        </FlavorTextOption>
    </FlavorTextDef>

